        pricing_overview: '<p>TextCortex operates an exceptionally intelligent Freemium "Creation" model. The Free tier grants users a daily recurring allowance of standard creations, making it wildly popular for casual users who just need to write a few emails. The "Lite" and "Unlimited" subscription tiers are strictly required for high-volume professionals, violently expanding the creation limits, unlocking massive PDF knowledge-base storage constraints, and allowing the deployment of the most expensive, elite LLM models (like GPT-4).</p>',
